Description: Siyarix — AI Cybersecurity Orchestration Agent
 Siyarix is an AI-native cybersecurity operations platform with
 autonomous execution, multi-agent framework, intelligent workflow
 orchestration, and advanced security tooling for offensive and
 defensive cybersecurity operations.
 .
 Features:
  * Autonomous AI-driven penetration testing
  * Multi-agent coordination for complex security workflows
  * 25+ security tool parsers (nmap, nuclei, metasploit, etc.)
  * Built-in OPSEC, stealth, and kill-switch mechanisms
  * Advanced reporting and compliance frameworks
  * Distributed orchestration with worker pools
  * Real-time dashboards and telemetry
